{"type":"nodegraph-data","nodes":[{"id":"authority-boundary-root","type":"markdown","label":"Authority Boundary Task","position":{"x":-540,"y":-320},"width":520,"height":260,"visible":true,"showLabel":true,"data":{"markdown":"# Authority Boundary\n\nDefine how **manifest authority** scopes a graph, how cross-graph links behave, and what is allowed to mutate.\n\n**Goal:** portability without silent overreach.\n\n**Outcome:** a contract + validator behavior + UI cues."}},{"id":"authority-boundary-definition","type":"markdown","label":"Definition","position":{"x":40,"y":-320},"width":420,"height":240,"visible":true,"showLabel":true,"data":{"markdown":"## Definition\n\n- **Authority boundary** is the scope where a manifest has jurisdiction.\n- Boundary is rooted at the **first manifest** encountered in the file.\n- Nodes reachable from that manifest (via structure edges) are **in-bounds**."}},{"id":"authority-boundary-structure-edges","type":"markdown","label":"Structure Edge Set","position":{"x":40,"y":-20},"width":420,"height":260,"visible":true,"showLabel":true,"data":{"markdown":"## Structure Edge Set (Reachability)\n\n**Count as structural:**\n- `contains`\n- `child` (legacy alias of `contains`)\n- `cluster` / `member` (cluster membership)\n\n**Not structural:**\n- `relates`, `references`, `dependsOn`, `requires`, `precedes`,\n  `derivesFrom`, `constrains`, `equivalentTo`, `transformsTo`, `conflictsWith`\n\n**Rule:** only structural edges extend authority."}},{"id":"authority-boundary-in-out","type":"markdown","label":"In-Bounds vs Out-Of-Bounds","position":{"x":40,"y":290},"width":420,"height":260,"visible":true,"showLabel":true,"data":{"markdown":"## In-Bounds vs Out-Of-Bounds\n\n**In-bounds**:\n- Manifest governs contracts + validation\n- Mutations allowed\n\n**Out-of-bounds**:\n- Read-only references\n- No mutation or contract enforcement\n- Render as linked/external"}},{"id":"authority-boundary-links","type":"markdown","label":"Cross-Boundary Links","position":{"x":-540,"y":-20},"width":520,"height":260,"visible":true,"showLabel":true,"data":{"markdown":"## Cross-Boundary Links\n\n- Edges may cross boundaries (links are allowed).\n- Crossing edges do **not** imply authority.\n- Links are navigation, not ownership.\n\n**Rule:** reference is OK; mutation is not."}},{"id":"authority-boundary-clusters","type":"markdown","label":"Cluster Membership Constraint","position":{"x":-540,"y":290},"width":520,"height":240,"visible":true,"showLabel":true,"data":{"markdown":"## Cluster Membership Constraint\n\n- Clusters may only list **local nodes** (same file / same authority scope).\n- External node IDs are ignored and should warn.\n\n**No backdoor imports via grouping.**"}},{"id":"authority-boundary-navigation","type":"markdown","label":"Authority vs Navigation","position":{"x":-540,"y":620},"width":520,"height":260,"visible":true,"showLabel":true,"data":{"markdown":"## Authority vs Navigation\n\n- **Authority never moves implicitly.**\n- You may *navigate* to any node (even with another manifest).\n- Switching authority is explicit (\"Open graph\" / \"Enter manifest\").\n\n**2D:** prompt to open when selecting another manifest.\n**VR:** portal/enter action to switch context."}},{"id":"authority-boundary-enforcement","type":"markdown","label":"Enforcement + UX","position":{"x":-540,"y":920},"width":520,"height":260,"visible":true,"showLabel":true,"data":{"markdown":"## Enforcement + UX\n\n- Validator warns on mutations targeting out-of-bounds nodes.\n- UI shows **external/linked** badge on out-of-bounds nodes.\n- Optional: warning snackbar when attempting edits across boundary.\n\n**Never silently mutate outside boundary.**"}},{"id":"authority-boundary-execution","type":"markdown","label":"Execution Gate","position":{"x":40,"y":620},"width":420,"height":240,"visible":true,"showLabel":true,"data":{"markdown":"## Execution Gate\n\n- **Viewing is free. Execution is gated.**\n- Foreign graphs can be inspected without adopting their rules.\n- Running scripts/skills requires explicit authority switch.\n\n**Analogy:** read vs import/run in a programming language."}},{"id":"authority-boundary-open","type":"markdown","label":"Open Questions","position":{"x":40,"y":920},"width":420,"height":240,"visible":true,"showLabel":true,"data":{"markdown":"## Open Questions\n\n**Resolved**\n1. Manifest does **not** define custom boundary rules.\n2. Structure edge set defines reachability (see above).\n3. Cross-boundary links are represented by proxy/port nodes.\n4. Files can contain multiple graphs, but each graph has one manifest."}}],"edges":[{"id":"edge-authority-root-definition","type":"dataFlow","source":"authority-boundary-root","target":"authority-boundary-definition","label":"defines","style":{"width":2,"dash":[],"curved":true},"data":{}},{"id":"edge-authority-definition-structure","type":"dataFlow","source":"authority-boundary-definition","target":"authority-boundary-structure-edges","label":"requires","style":{"width":2,"dash":[],"curved":true},"data":{}},{"id":"edge-authority-structure-inout","type":"dataFlow","source":"authority-boundary-structure-edges","target":"authority-boundary-in-out","label":"scopes","style":{"width":2,"dash":[],"curved":true},"data":{}},{"id":"edge-authority-root-links","type":"dataFlow","source":"authority-boundary-root","target":"authority-boundary-links","label":"allows","style":{"width":2,"dash":[],"curved":true},"data":{}},{"id":"edge-authority-links-clusters","type":"dataFlow","source":"authority-boundary-links","target":"authority-boundary-clusters","label":"limits","style":{"width":2,"dash":[],"curved":true},"data":{}},{"id":"edge-authority-clusters-navigation","type":"dataFlow","source":"authority-boundary-clusters","target":"authority-boundary-navigation","label":"separates","style":{"width":2,"dash":[],"curved":true},"data":{}},{"id":"edge-authority-navigation-execution","type":"dataFlow","source":"authority-boundary-navigation","target":"authority-boundary-execution","label":"gates","style":{"width":2,"dash":[],"curved":true},"data":{}},{"id":"edge-authority-execution-enforcement","type":"dataFlow","source":"authority-boundary-execution","target":"authority-boundary-enforcement","label":"requires","style":{"width":2,"dash":[],"curved":true},"data":{}},{"id":"edge-authority-enforcement-open","type":"dataFlow","source":"authority-boundary-enforcement","target":"authority-boundary-open","label":"questions","style":{"width":2,"dash":[],"curved":true},"data":{}}],"timestamp":"2026-01-27T00:00:00.000Z","nodeCount":10,"edgeCount":9}
